1) We need a smart contract to deposit tokens into the game. That is, a person makes a deposit and the game tokens are transferred to the game account. Then all calculations, such as adding tokens for winning, take place already in the database.  

2) Smart contract for stacking, after which the game starts. Stacking activates a series of 5 wins that must be completed within 24 hours to receive a reward ( chest ). NFT with a very small probability. Basically, tokens fall out of the chest. 

3) smart contract to withdraw tokens from the game to the player's wallet. At the beginning of the withdrawal commission is 30%, then decreases by 1.5% every 2 days. The minimum commission is 15%.

4) smart contract that allows you to exchange a token for a chest within the game. From the chest, depending on its rarity, falls different rarity NFTs

5) token smart contract
